{"tid":542549,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"擺低你同初戀嘅故事","createTime":"2018-01-27T14:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T16:19:36.000Z","uid":163305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1df9aa4d618c39387c33fead2f9bab052c2cb309","tid":542549,"uid":163305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"果陣中學<br />\n我係一個band3 日日好得閒嘅學生<br />\n而佢係名校嘅學生<br />\n當我想帶佢周圍去玩果陣 佢話想專心讀書<br />\n雖然係名校 但係佢成績係倒數幾個<br />\n而且屋企逼得佢好重要 佢係單親家庭<br />\n老媽都想佢入大學 搵份好工 <br />\n結果佢博命讀書無時間理我 而且好大壓力<br />\n就同我分手<br />\n仲話 我唔絕點令你死心 其實我都好愛你 對唔住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e8a868261bad765d8b620a04e4eb98c3252dfb","tid":542549,"uid":22455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"好想分享 不過一開始回憶<br />\n就好心痛 所以都係收皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8389c21854f50c6dedaf6b9a23712e3d9f3a3a","tid":542549,"uid":163305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e8a868261bad765d8b620a04e4eb98c3252dfb","tid":542549,"uid":22455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"好想分享 不過一開始回憶<br />\n就好心痛 所以都係收皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"欣賞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf45b3d543ba00d8c923cb81eae7d64d2859fb2","tid":542549,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"咁樓主你而家點？佢而家點？"},{"pid":"5f0628ce66e0f4a33508193ff17706bd2d8fdb61","tid":542549,"uid":163305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf45b3d543ba00d8c923cb81eae7d64d2859fb2","tid":542549,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"咁樓主你而家點？佢而家點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"無聯絡啦 之前有打聽過佢啲同學 都話佢日日西口西臉好似好大壓力咁 我有每年講一次生日快樂 但係都無理到我<img src=\"